main event: Bright lights were observed moving erratically for 3 minutes at Webb AFB, Texas.
interesting points: The lights were reported as bright white and changed positions before vanishing., The lights were reported to the control tower, which could not detect them on radar., The probable sighting was attributed to Venus., The sighting lasted for about 3 minutes., The observation was made by qualified tower operators.
sighted object: two to three bright lights in the sky
witness description: qualified control tower operators including TSGT and CAPT
